CREATE TABLE `Addresses` (
    `Id` char(36) COLLATE ascii_general_ci NOT NULL,
    `AppUserId` char(36) COLLATE ascii_general_ci NOT NULL,
    `AddressName` varchar(100) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NOT NULL,
    `FirstName` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NOT NULL,
    `LastName` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NOT NULL,
    `PhoneNumber` varchar(15) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NOT NULL,
    `AlternativePhoneNumber` varchar(15) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NULL,
    `Email` varchar(100) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NOT NULL,
    `City` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NOT NULL,
    `District` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NOT NULL,
    `Neighborhood` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NOT NULL,
    `AddressInfo` varchar(250) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NOT NULL,
    `IsInvoiceAddress` tinyint(1) NOT NULL,
    `InvoiceAddressName` varchar(100) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NULL,
    `InvoiceFirstName` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NULL,
    `InvoiceLastName` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NULL,
    `InvoicePhoneNumber` varchar(15) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NULL,
    `InvoiceEmail` varchar(100) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NULL,
    `InvoiceCity` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NULL,
    `InvoiceDistrict` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NULL,
    `InvoiceNeighborhood` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NULL,
    `InvoiceAddressInfo` varchar(250) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NULL,
    `CreatedBy` longtext CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NOT NULL,
    `ModifiedBy` longtext CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NULL,
    `DeletedBy` longtext CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 NULL,
    `CreatedDate` datetime(6) NOT NULL,
    `ModifiedDate` datetime(6) NULL,
    `DeletedDate` datetime(6) NULL,
    `IsDeleted` tinyint(1) NOT NULL,
    CONSTRAINT `PK_Addresses` PRIMARY KEY (`Id`),
    CONSTRAINT `FK_Addresses_AspNetUsers_AppUserId` FOREIGN KEY (`AppUserId`) REFERENCES `AspNetUsers` (`Id`) ON DELETE CASCADE
) CHARACTER SET=utf8mb4;
